BAM ğŸ’¥ â€” Youâ€™re inside 172.16.8.20 without ever directly touching it.

ğŸ” Whatâ€™s Really Happening?
You canâ€™t reach 172.16.8.20 directly.

But 172.16.8.5 (your pivot) can.

So you make 172.16.8.5 act like a proxy for that port, and access that instead.

ğŸ§  Bonus Tip:
